Class StackHotel

  • java.lang.Object
    • Hotel
      • StackHotel
  • public class StackHotel
extends Hotel
    An implementation of the abstract class Hotel that uses a stack to store Guest objects. The last Guest to check in is the first to check out (LIFO).
    Version:
    02-29-2020
    Author:
    Feras Salous

        public Guest nextGuestToCheckOut()

      • checkOut
